    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_a0ed27de"><bpmn:text>Check exception in Art. 18 Abs. 1 lit. b&#10;Check exception in Art. 18 Abs. 1 lit. c&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Data is Accurate AND Limit</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
