    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_3a2b22a1"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Processing Was Lawful AND Limit</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
