    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_a9ce7edb"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Applies when: Permitted AND Consent Withdrawn AND Legitimate Interest AND High Risk to Individuals</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
